    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but some people say that renewables like wind and solar just arent enough to actually hit the net zero goals in time because they are too intermittent. if we dont use nuclear we might actually fail at stopping climate change entirely. dont you think that makes nuclear more of a necessity than just an option?",
